- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Facilities &amp; Features</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">1<!-- --> <!-- -->answer</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">1</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Rules &amp; Etiquette</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Events &amp; Parties</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Training</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a sidebar-card support-card\"><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a support-label\">Still stuck?</p><h3 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Chat with our team</h3><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Share your situation and we&#x27;ll recommend the best park, indoor option, or community meetup.</p><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a support-actions\"><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Contact us</a><a href=\"/signup\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a secondary\">Join community</a></div></div></aside><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-main\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-rail\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-eyebrow\">Popular right now</span><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Tap to jump to the full answer.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-question-circle\"></i>Where is the original Bar K located?</button></div></div><div role=\"list\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-accordion\"><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">01</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Where is the original Bar K located?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">The original Bar K is located in Kansas City, MO, right on the shore of the Missouri River.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">Facilities &amp; Features</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">The original Bar K is located in Kansas City, MO, right on the shore of the Missouri River. It features a massive indoor and outdoor off-leash park.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->Facilities &amp; Features</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">02</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Does Missouri have water park options for dogs?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">Yes!</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">Planning Your Visit</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Yes! Twin Lakes in Columbia and several parks in the St. Louis area (like Southwest City) offer water features or dedicated pond access for dogs.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->Planning Your Visit</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"state-section alt\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"cta-band\"><div><h3>Help us expand <!-- -->Missouri<!-- --> coverage</h3><p>Submit your favorite spot and we’ll review it for inclusion in the directory.</p></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>List your park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/cities\"><i class=\"bi bi-compass\"></i>Explore cities</a></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"footer-new\"><div class=\"footer-container\"><div class=\"footer-grid\"><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">IndoorDogPark</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/about\">About us</a></li><li><a href=\"/partners\">Partners</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Discover</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/\">Browse parks</a></li><li><a href=\"/how-it-works\">How it works</a></li><li><a href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Park Owners</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/list-your-park\">List your park</a></li><li><a href=\"/owner-resources\">Owner resources</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Support</h4><ul class=\"footer-links\"><li><a href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a></li><li><a href=\"/faq\">FAQ</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"footer-column col-span-full md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1\"><h4 class=\"footer-heading\">Join the Pack</h4><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm text-white/70\">Get the latest indoor dog park news and updates.</p><div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4 backdrop-blur-sm\"><div class=\" w-full\"><div class=\"mb-4 flex p-1 rounded-xl relative bg-white/10 border border-white/15\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Newsletter audience\"><div class=\"absolute inset-y-1 w-[calc(50%-4px)] rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out bg-white shadow-sm left-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><button type=\"button\" class=\"relative z-10 w-1/2 py-2 text-sm font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200 text-gray-900\" role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" aria-controls=\"_R_1qdav5ubr5b_-panel\"